          <span class="font-semibold text-lg text-white">Kunal Das</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 max-w-xs">
          Developer Advocate APAC at CAST AI. Passionate about cloud-native technologies, Kubernetes optimization, and building scalable infrastructure.
        </p>
        <a
          href="mailto:contactkunalmail.region943@passinbox.com"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-slate-400 hover:text-cyan-300 transition-colors mt-3"
        >
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
